---
title: Vietnamese-Style Shrimp Lettuce Wraps Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: These lettuce wraps are packed with bright flavors and crisp textures for a light, satisfying family-style meal that’s on the table in just 15 minutes! You’ll start by boiling a pot of rice noodles, then quick-pickling crisp shredded carrots. Meanwhile you’ll sizzle up garlicky shrimp and bring it all together in a savory, tart ponzu and lime sauce with a touch of brown sugar. Serve all these delicious elements—shrimp, noodles, lettuce leaves, pickled carrots, scallion greens, lime wedges, ponzu sauce, and peanuts—in separate bowls, and let everyone create their own dinner masterpieces.
